content: Packing up from Japan, I'm a mix of excited and uncertain. This cultural tapestry has woven new threads into my identity. Now, back to NYC to blend East with West, maybe even host an event where they meet. 🗽🇯🇵
raw_content: As I pack my bags from Japan, ready to return to NYC, I'm filled with both excitement and a touch of uncertainty. My time here has been a cultural tapestry, weaving new threads into the fabric of who I am. Now, I aim to bring this rich experience back to the city that never sleeps, and perhaps, organize an event where East truly meets West. 🗽🇯🇵
